  "title": "Car Mechanic (Class 3) #76247",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Towing Service</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Car Mechanic (Class 3)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Redhill</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday – Friday), Day Shift 6.30am-3.30pm; Night shift 3.30pm-11.30am</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary up to $3500 + AWS + Incentive + Allowance</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Respond promptly to job assignments and perform mechanic services on-site.</li><li>Restart vehicles for AA members and corporate customers facing breakdowns.</li><li>Follow safety practices when handling breakdown cases.</li><li>Complete documentation as required for vehicle recovery procedures.</li><li>Provide basic customer service during all assignments.</li><li>Secure all sales proceeds and deposit them at the Call Centre after each shift.</li><li>Restock service van batteries after making sales.</li><li>Perform daily checks on service vehicles before operations.</li><li>Upskill to support corrective and preventive maintenance and EV charger servicing.</li><li>Carry out other tasks as assigned by supervisors.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Valid Singapore Class 3 driving licence required.</li><li>Minimum qualification: NTC in Vehicle Mechanic or higher.</li><li>Willing to work rotating shifts, including weekends and public holidays.</li><li>Experience in vehicle recovery is an advantage.</li><li>Knowledge of basic vehicle repair or maintenance is a plus.</li><li>No experience required if willing to learn and have a positive attitude.</li><li>Able to start work immediately or at short notice is preferred</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76247 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
